FT  29 DEC 93 / World News in Brief: Truck drivers head home
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Three British truck drivers headed home from Turkey after being freed from
jail. A court found there was not enough evidence to detain them for
allegedly having false documents as part of an export fraud. They had been
held for four weeks.
