FT  23 DEC 93 / UK Company News: Aitken Hume - Correction
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The issue of December 1 described Mr Lee Ming Tee as chairman of Allied
Group. He resigned on September 30. The fact that, as the article stated, Mr
Brian O'Connor, his successor, was named in a report from the Financial
Secretary of Hong Kong should not be read as suggesting that he was
criticised in it. We apologise for any suggestion to the contrary.
